author: The Current
description:
Watch Royel Otis tell a skydiving version of their origin story at The Current
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

Australian band Royel Otis — anchored by the duo of Royel Maddell and Otis Pavlovic — visited The Current for a conversation with host Jessica Paxton. Part of the chat included this skydiving version of the band's origin story ... true? ... or not?
